      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Ready for your next adventure? This well-loved vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained to keep you moving! It features a clean, comfortable interior and a smooth ride that demonstrates its solid service history. It's a fantastic, dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality car that still looks great and performs even better!",
